{"tid":1892763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔笑夠日本未? 分化夠未?","createTime":"2020-02-22T18:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T19:16:45.000Z","uid":311385,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04bd08a99016b6877e7a3a1b6e47996686ede576","tid":1892763,"uid":311385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:01:06.000Z","msg":"我唔係好識講說話，但係日本人係過去大半年，都有關心香港，幫香港打氣，TWITTER又好，Facebook又好。仲有日本人特登嚟香港整COFFEE 免費派俾人飲。<br />\n<br />\n今日竟然換嚟，俾連登仔笑呀！<br />\n<br />\n香港人今次防疫工作比較強，唔係因為你叻呀，係因為SARS 03年死咗好多醫生護士，換返嚟嘅經驗呀！而人地日本真係大半個世紀都未面前過咁嘅傳染病毒。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔你地係咪應該用TWITTER，分享返經驗俾日本民眾呀? 話返俾佢聽今次有幾嚴重，而唔係喺度笑人地。<br />\n定係連登仔反送中文宣先記得人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33e40d880f1df87b45f8aa30437b6486bbd5e4c","tid":1892763,"uid":242605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻煩各位手足幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYouTube 戰線認真要打</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極速訂閱 黃色頻道</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9viZgif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9viZgif.gif&h=d9687fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCdgu47O1Wlw&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=569e1c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw</a><br />\n［黃藍YOUTUBE大戰正式開打］極簡單方法支持黃YOUTUBER (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab4dd559a46c14d1d718fecb90c31a962c3726b6","tid":1892763,"uid":311385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，認同嘅幫手推推"},{"pid":"552cda4e3a388d19aa480f29fdd74f56d63a0651","tid":1892763,"uid":25771,